Physical Activity and Sport ActOrder Designating the Minister of Health to be the Minister for the Purposes of the Physical Activity and Sport Act in Respect of Physical Activity and the Minister of State (Sport) to be the Minister for the Purposes of that Act in Respect of SportOrder (1) designating the Minister of HEALTH, a member of the King’s Privy Council for Canada, as the Minister for the purposes of the PHYSICAL ACTIVITY AND SPORT ACT in respect of physical activity; and (2) designating the Minister of STATE (SPORT), a member of the King's Privy Council for Canada, to be the Minister for the purposes of the PHYSICAL ACTIVITY AND SPORT ACT in respect of sport.Registration: SI/2025-0083 Publication Date: 2025-06-04

Physical Activity and Sport Act
Physical Activity and Sport Act
subject: Order Designating the Minister of Health to be the Minister for the Purposes of the Physical Activity and Sport Act in Respect of Physical Activity and the Minister of State (Sport) to be the Minister for the Purposes of that Act in Respect of Sport
precis: Order (1) designating the Minister of HEALTH, a member of the King’s Privy Council for Canada, as the Minister for the purposes of the PHYSICAL ACTIVITY AND SPORT ACT in respect of physical activity; and (2) designating the Minister of STATE (SPORT), a member of the King's Privy Council for Canada, to be the Minister for the purposes of the PHYSICAL ACTIVITY AND SPORT ACT in respect of sport.
